name: TellJokes
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny jokes
des:
Life is not that serious as we think. Don't believe me? Ask Alexa to tell some fun jokes using this "funny jokes" Alexa Skill.
Usage:
1) Ask Alexa to open "Funny Jokes"
2) Say yes to hear one, otherwise say no if you change your mind.
3) That's it. Alexa will come back to you with a new joke.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
